description: AMUNDI ETF STOXX EUROPE 50 UCITS ETF seeks to replicate as closely as possible the performance of the STOXX Europe 50 Index, whether the trend is rising or falling. This ETF enables investors to benefit from an exposure to leading stocks covering European countries, with a single transaction. For further information, please also refer to the fund prospectus.
name: Amundi ETF Stoxx Europe 50 UCITS ETF
